{"id": 3057, "title": "Ticket #3057: Blahp needs improved escaping of job arguments", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe blahp doesn't do sufficient escaping of characters that appear in the job's arguments when passing them to the submit script. Some characters, like parentheses can be interpreted by the shell.\n\n<p>Brian Bockelman has a patch that partially solves the problem. When supplying the patch, he said \"Here's a quick way to do it.  I guess we should consider escaping all the characters mentioned in <code>man wordexp</code>.\"</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body><blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"../files/577/blahp-escape.patch\">blahp-escape.patch</a>\n498 bytes added by jfrey on 2012-Jun-14 20:29:09 UTC.\n<br/>\nPatch to properly escape some characters in a job's arguments when passing from the blahp to its submit script.<br/>\n</li></ul>\n</blockquote></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Sep-06 10:36</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=33287\">[33287]</a></span>: reformat 7.9.1 version history item to make characters easier to read ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=3057\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3057'); return false;\" title=\"Blahp needs improved escaping of job arguments\">#3057</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Aug-07 14:33</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=32993\">[32993]</a></span>: blahp version history. <span cla